        adresa varchar(255),

        roles varchar(255),
        sifra varchar(255),
        primary key (id)
    ) engine=MyISAM

    ) engine=MyISAM

    FROM
        porudzbina p

        p.id=? 
    GROUP BY
        p.id

        s.kolicina*a.cena 
    FROM
        porudzbina p 
    INNER JOIN

        artikal a 
            on s.artikal_id = a.id 
    WHERE
        p.id=? 
    GROUP BY
        p.id

    FROM

        p.id=?

        p.id

    SELECT
        SUM(s.kolicina*a.cena) 
    FROM
        porudzbina p 
    INNER JOIN
        stavka s 
            on s.porudzbina_id = p.id 
    INNER JOIN
        artikal a 
            on s.artikal_id = a.id 
    WHERE
        p.id=? 
    GROUP BY
        p.id

2022-01-13 17:33:52.164 DEBUG 2408 --- [http-nio-8080-exec-2] o.h.SQL                                  : 
    SELECT
        SUM(s.kolicina*a.cena) 
    FROM
        porudzbina p 
    INNER JOIN
        stavka s 
            on s.porudzbina_id = p.id 
    INNER JOIN
        artikal a 
            on s.artikal_id = a.id 
    WHERE
        p.id=? 
    GROUP BY
        p.id
